 * links.column1_items => 栏目1链接:textarea:Personal Banking=>/personal\r\nBusiness Solutions=>/business\r\nInvestments=>/invest\r\nGlobal Transfers=>/transfers|格式：名称=>链接，一行一个
 * links.column2_title => 栏目2标题:text:Company
 * links.column2_items => 栏目2链接:textarea:About Us=>/about\r\nCareers=>/careers\r\nPress=>/press\r\nPartners=>/partners|格式：名称=>链接，一行一个
 * links.column3_title => 栏目3标题:text:Legal
 * links.column3_items => 栏目3链接:textarea:Privacy Policy=>/privacy\r\nTerms of Service=>/terms\r\nCompliance=>/compliance\r\nSecurity=>/security|格式：名称=>链接，一行一个
